# Line-ending normalization.
#
# Committing this file overrides each contributor's local `core.autocrlf`
# setting, guaranteeing consistent line endings for everyone regardless of OS
# or Git configuration (see GitHub docs: "Configuring Git to handle line
# endings"). Text files are stored as LF in the repository and checked out as
# LF in every working tree, which matches the Biome/Ultracite formatter default.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicitly mark binary assets so their bytes are never altered.
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif  binary
*.ico  binary
*.webp binary
*.avif binary
*.woff  binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf  binary
*.otf  binary
*.eot  binary
*.pdf  binary
